    </button>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ══ BODY ══ -->
<div class="nb-body">

    <!-- TOC -->
  <nav class="nb-toc" id="toc">
    <div class="toc-section-label">단원 목차</div>

    <a class="toc-item" onclick="tocGo('s1', this)">
      <span>1️⃣ 반복문 복습</span><span class="toc-badge concept">개념+예시+실습</span>
